      <title>亞馬遜將斥資近 90 億美元擴大新加坡雲端基礎設施</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-spend-9-bln-expand-cloud-infra-singapore-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亞馬遜網路服務 (AWS) 週二表示，亞馬遜公司計劃在未來四年內斥資 120 億新元（合 88.8 億美元）擴大其在新加坡的雲端運算基礎設施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-spend-9-bln-expand-cloud-infra-singapore-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 03:07:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亞洲股市因降息押注而上漲；澳洲央行可能轉向鷹派</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由於對美國降息的信心重燃，亞洲股市週二創下 15 個月高位，而交易員則等待當天晚些時候在澳洲舉行的政策會議，並密切關注日圓貶值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 01:59:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麥格理預計即將到來的美國和歐盟選舉中保護主義將會抬頭</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/macquarie-eyes-rise-protectionism-upcoming-us-eu-elections-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球金融集團麥格理集團(Macquarie Group)執行長謝馬拉·維克拉馬納亞克(Shemara Wikramanayake)週二表示，保護主義政策在今年美國和歐盟選舉中獲勝的可能性對企業構成風險，全球金融集團麥格理集團(Macquarie Group)正密切關注此一風險。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/macquarie-eyes-rise-protectionism-upcoming-us-eu-elections-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 01:18:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>儘管有乾預威脅，日圓還是走軟，澳元在澳洲央行之前保持穩定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-eases-despite-intervention-threat-aussie-steady-before-rba-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[儘管日本官員在上週兩輪疑似美元拋售幹預後發出了新的警告，但由於利差巨大，日圓兌美元週二繼續走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-eases-despite-intervention-threat-aussie-steady-before-rba-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 01:02:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
